The measures of Constans , who then resided in Dacia , were directed with more prudence and ability . 
On the news of his brother's invasion , he detached a select and disciplined body of his Illyrian troops , proposing to follow them in person , with the remainder of his forces . 
But the conduct of his lieutenants soon terminated the unnatural contest . 
The causes and the events of this civil war are related with much perplexity and contradiction . 
I have chiefly followed Zonaras and the younger Victor . 
