The primates of Rome , Alexandria , Antioch , Carthage , and afterwards Constantinople , who exercised a more ample jurisdiction , convened the numerous assembly of their dependent bishops . 
But the convocation of great and extraordinary synods was the prerogative of the emperor alone . 
The session , which lasted about two months , was frequently honored by the presence of the emperor . 
