You persecute , says he , those heretics who do not mourn the dead man precisely in the way which you approve . 
He shows himself a tolerable theologian but he maintains that the Christian Trinity is not derived from the doctrine of Paul , of Jesus , or of Moses . 
As soon as Gallus was invested with the honors of the purple , Julian was permitted to breathe the air of freedom , of literature , and of Paganism . 
The deities of Olympus , as they are painted by the immortal bard , imprint themselves on the minds which are the least addicted to superstitious credulity . 
The weakness of polytheism was , in some measure , excused by the moderation of its claims and the devotion of the Pagans was not incompatible with the most licentious scepticism . 
