The wisest of the Pagans censured this extravagant superstition , which affected to despise the restraints of prudence and decency . 
Encouraged by the example , the exhortations , the liberality , of their pious sovereign , the cities and families resumed the practice of their neglected ceremonies . 
The jurisdiction of the supreme pontiff , more especially after that office had been united with the Imperial dignity , comprehended the whole extent of the Roman empire . 
