The pride of royalty was humbled in the dust he took his repasts on the ground and the disorder of his hair expressed the grief and anxiety of his mind . 
He was astonished by the inflexible firmness of a hero , who remembered , most unfortunately for himself and for his country , that Alexander had uniformly rejected the propositions of Darius . 
