Chapter XXV Reigns Of Jovian And Valentinian , Division Of The Empire . 
Part I. The Government And Death Of Jovian . 
Election Of Valentinian , Who Associates His Brother Valens , And Makes The Final Division Of The Eastern And Western Empires . 
His Two Sons , Gratian And Valentinian II . 
