Valentinian resolved to execute severe vengeance on the whole body of the nation . 
Count Sebastian , with the bands of Italy and Illyricum , was ordered to invade their country , most probably on the side of Rhaetia . 
The life of Valentinian was exposed to imminent danger by the intrepid curiosity with which he persisted to explore some secret and unguarded path . 
At the signal of the general assault , the Roman troops encompassed and ascended the mountain of Solicinium on three different sides . 
After this signal victory , Valentinian returned to his winter quarters at Treves where he indulged the public joy by the exhibition of splendid and triumphal games . 
