But their pride was humbled , and their progress was checked , by the arms and policy of Vouti , the fifth emperor of the powerful dynasty of the Han . 
Instead of confining himself to the timid operations of a defensive war , his lieutenants penetrated many hundred miles into the country of the Huns . 
These losses , however , were compensated by splendid and decisive success . 
The Chinese generals improved the superiority which they derived from the temper of their arms , their chariots of war , and the service of their Tartar auxiliaries . 
One of the princes of the nation was urged , by fear and ambition , to retire towards the South with eight hords , which composed between forty and fifty thousand families . 
From the time of this fatal schism , the Huns of the North continued to languish about fifty years till they were oppressed on every side by their foreign and domestic enemies . 
The proud inscription of a column , erected on a lofty mountain , announced to posterity , that a Chinese army had marched seven hundred miles into the heart of their country . 
